Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.67,0:01:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…毕娜可都告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们身体的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:01:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍先生 能来帮个忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那稍后慢慢聊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.07,0:02:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们修好的收音机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后都挺好用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.10,0:02:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没杂音了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 都怪我们跟高奈罗找茬…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你们揭发了恶行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市才恢复了理智
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有过暴动什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全镇人齐心协力努力复兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛弃一切隔阂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝塞 麻烦你照顾温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们也去帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 尤基
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干完活再吃更美味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了快来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！放开我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 刚才那是你儿子？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是久别重逢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放着他不管没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 其实我多年前就离家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应该也不信任我这个父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道该说些什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来干活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我来搬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:04:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉小姐 水温怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼 多久没泡过澡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换洗的衣服放在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝塞小姐真是个好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你可真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么年轻就已经是独当一面的机械铠专家了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德的腿也是你做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算是青梅竹马的交情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害 是你为爱德做了支撑起他的腿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绕个圈子也是支撑我站起来的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以温莉小姐也是我的恩人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「能让死去的恋人复活」…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.19,0:04:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻信这种奇迹之术 我投身于雷托教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德和阿尔来到这个小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揭穿了教主的骗局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然失去了一直以来的依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我很绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后爱德就骂了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我用自己的脚站起来继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 那家伙总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么就不能稍微温柔点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很温柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是爱德的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你也明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏他 我和这个城市都清醒了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不依靠奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都决心靠自己的力量重新站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了爱德和阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着军队那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:06:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却闯进一个奇怪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 格利德先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.67,0:06:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦理是可以随时代和个人而改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是因为那种理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了防止个人拥有强力的军队啊 少将
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是人 是人偶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 在具有人形的容器里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附着上灵魂并制造出士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全服从我们的命令作战的最强士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是不死的军团
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能请教个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用来附着的灵魂 要从哪里弄来？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我们践踏过…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是即将践踏的国家的人身上弄来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战场将成为入手大量灵魂的狩猎场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央好可怕 残忍 不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格利德先生不可能在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下通道？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我想确认这城市地下有没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一定有 要把它…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 去没人的地方谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来雷奥尔是为了阻止国土炼成阵发动？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.40,0:07:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后看到爸爸在这里 真是大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时也觉得很幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在中央的地下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见过一个和爸爸一模一样的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他不可能和爸爸完全无关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定你会知道他是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗 阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若我是那边的人怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没想过我会一股脑告诉那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你这么信任我 我很欣慰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这种人 他也还当我是父亲来信赖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也该相信儿子 把一切都告诉他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来就话长了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想让爱德华一起听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一位请
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想从国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华·艾尔利克的研究费户头提款
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是本人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是代理人 有委托书和签名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是班克斯银行北区分店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人从国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华·艾尔利克的户头提取了现金
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个自称代理人的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 特征是壮实的大汉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 治疗费
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 确实没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 居然狮子开大口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 算上封口费这个数刚好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 不深究我们的事就帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达利乌斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧 被发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 兵大哥 哪儿不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在找人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个病人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人住院吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面还有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住院的病患就你一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是去银行的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 是这医院的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双手慢慢从棉被里拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近有没有见过什么陌生人出入医院？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特征是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 举起双手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿红色风衣 金发绑着麻花辫的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矮子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点 谁干的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 哈里…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科恩 哈里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 快回话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 你怎么全部一个人解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你体力还没恢复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别当我是病人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经完全恢复 火力全开了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙照顾了 医生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气了 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可不想再招惹麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们凭红色风衣和麻花辫来搜索的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来暂时保持这身打扮比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧 增援吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举起手来 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的小孩快退开 很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许动的是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕我毙了这小子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个交通工具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猩猩兄 有追兵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快被追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是北方军
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走雪道上跑不赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 后面怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 紧跟着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面右转 进横道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠 搞不清楚状况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去麻烦立即回头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上…上哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是从那个交叉路口拐弯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼 顺利甩掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你重新炼个朴素点的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥 这样不是很威风吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了快改吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了快改掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啦 你们对我的品味有意见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意见大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又无处可去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因对金布利那家伙一时大意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是被拖足了后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知阿尔那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和温莉他们顺利汇合了没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 钢仔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.28,0:15:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 总之我需要情报
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须跟阿尔他们汇合才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里才能汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是阿尔会去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想一想 仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸是奴隶 还是贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然难以置信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然听到这种话还能接受的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是脑子有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 看来我就是那种脑子有问题的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:16:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你接受能力好强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 我是吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 可能因为自己也是这种身体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 不会死是什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么感觉…这身体虽然挺方便的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就是受不了重要的人先我而去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 爸爸是贤者之石 不算正常的身体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是正常人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然和贤者之石以及灵魂融合在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但核心依然是我这个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是待在中央的那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却是装在长得像我的皮囊里的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮囊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以破坏那皮囊 应该就能打倒他了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒…对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是不是打算利用这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重现克塞尔克塞斯的惨剧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不立即阻止他们就不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们居然能调查到这个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是逆转的炼成阵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最快的方法就是破坏地下通道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要把这里地下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下有个超级厉害 叫普莱德人造人的守着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不尽快的话 他们的炼成阵…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕早就完成了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不到那个日子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个日子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要光看下面 看看头上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能看出一些东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳神雷托？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在等待一个特殊的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 我到底做了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错 我喜欢有活力的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看守地下的工作很无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最欢迎你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最强的盾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那口气 那笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:19:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 你竟敢模仿格利德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我就是格利德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然知道我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强欲的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 这世上的一切都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要钱 也要女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有地位和名誉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这世上的一切我都想要」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.98,0:19:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…不 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格利德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吗 为什么变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊 达布利斯的彼得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了同伴的脸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达布利斯 哦是吗是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想起来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 那大概是以前的格利德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格利德…先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.26,0:19:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同…伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的任务是消灭入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.56,0:20:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是堕落到家了啊 格利德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然对同伴下手 你到底在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是…什么同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这记忆是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敢说那叫彼得的说的都是谎言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是以前那格利德的记忆 不是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为何如此痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我清醒点啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这么稀里糊涂的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的灵魂就要夺回这个身体了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前那格利德的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就抹消了记忆 净化掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去的一切早就忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘得掉才怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓同伴 是由灵魂联系在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经融入灵魂的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能轻易抹消的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.75,0:21:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂在呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你舍弃了灵魂的亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格利德 你还说什么要获得一切的强欲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.03,0:21:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是听不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.82,0:23:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.66,0:23:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在你这么大的时候看过的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.20,0:23:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是环游世界的冒险家的故事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.39,0:23:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.22,0:23:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.17,0:24:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.40,0:24:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已无人能阻止这愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.78,0:24:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存活下来的将是自己还是对方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.98,0:24:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结局的尽头将展示怎样的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.50,0:24:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.07,0:24:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.82,0:24:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第45集 约定之日
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.02,0:24:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集结吧 志同道合之人
